---
description: One task per worktree; workers stay inside the assigned path.
globs: "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

# Worktree Scope

- Branch naming: `task/<task_id>`.
- Worktree path pattern: `../worktrees/<repo-name>__<task_id>`.
- Workers edit only inside that worktree for the assigned task.
- Do not start nested subagents for the same task.
